{"tid":2353809,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"坪石邨公屋戶擁1,600萬大埔地皮房產　瞞報資產被判監14日","createTime":"2021-01-05T04:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T11:18:03.000Z","uid":99885,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4b88c0658a1570f9e80cbe8b01b743673bd3254f","tid":2353809,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T04:35:31.000Z","msg":"案情指，去年該公屋居民填寫入息及資產申報表時，申報並無擁有土地及物業，並聲稱其家庭總資產淨值不超逾現行公屋入息限額100倍。其後經調查揭發，該名公屋居民案發時擁有一幅位於大埔的土地，並獲地政總署於2018年批出建屋牌照及於去年發出完工證，該土地及物業的價值為1,600萬元，並不符合租住公屋資格。<br />\n<br />\n該名公屋居民因忽略提供入息及資產申報表指明的詳情，違反了《房屋條例》第27（a）條，而被房屋署作出檢控。被告今日（4日）上午在觀塘裁判法院被裁定罪名成立。裁判官考慮到案情嚴重，即時判處被告監禁14天。"},{"pid":"ba3a51d80a28ce094e84b45390806c71507a1e64","tid":2353809,"uid":1550,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T04:36:42.000Z","msg":"裁判官考慮到案情嚴重，即時判處被告監禁14天。"},{"pid":"3fd9e06bc6116f1a90247dcef8e3c42eb0c317e1","tid":2353809,"uid":8308,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"14日監禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依D唔係詐騙??"},{"pid":"b9e428ce927a9c569e49f873e5a94082cf7ecb1b","tid":2353809,"uid":369011,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"判監14天<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ce02f5d044e17b32cb57d509c596092b3dd202","tid":2353809,"uid":357612,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b9e428ce927a9c569e49f873e5a94082cf7ecb1b","tid":2353809,"uid":369011,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"判監14天<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:58:50.000Z","msg":"十四個月都少la"},{"pid":"70864a552d7230c1b088ce2fa111a0f433ca7ddc","tid":2353809,"uid":289134,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"r